humanMachineDialogue.author: Memory Reasoning
humanMachineDialogue.text: According to the report, 26 lymph nodes were assessed and one of them was positive for carcinoma. This corresponds to N1 stage, as per Rule 12 (N1 indicates metastases in 1 to 3 axillary lymph nodes). The report also mentions that there is no evidence of malignancy in the other 25 lymph nodes, which supports this conclusion.
